Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:18.04,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}小さい光　Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:21:01.81,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}远古之光 Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:16.36,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}雾之夜 被那黑暗所困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:27.96,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}只有气息存在着周围
